==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Knowingly
<hw>Know"ing*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>With knowledge;
in a knowing manner; intelligently; consciously; deliberately; <as>as,
he would not <ex>knowingly</ex> offend</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Strype.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>By experience.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knowingness</ent>⟦br⟧
